<div class="section banner banner-short text-center">
  <img src="/img/hackedu_logo.png">
  <h3 class="white hackedu-logo"><a href="/">hackEDU's</a></h3>
  <h1 class="white title">Accept your invite</h1>
</div>
<div class="section projects text-center">
  <h1 class="white open-sans">The Venue</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-10 small-centered large-6 large-centered columns">
      <a href="http://www.galvanize.com/campuses/san-francisco-soma/">
        <div class="panel">
          <h1>Galvanize (SoMa)</h1>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="section summary text-center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered large-10 large-centered columns">
      <p>
        We're excited to let you know that your application has been accepted.
      </p>
      <p>
        Camp is from 9:20am to 4:00pm Monday through Friday. If you can't
        attend a session, make sure a parent lets a Hack Camp Facilitator know.
        The curriculum is not hard, but can be fast-paced at times. To prevent
        anyone from falling behind anyone with 2 unexcused absenses will be
        dropped from the program. The deadline to pay your tuition is at 8pm on
        Tuesday the 26th.
      </p>
      <p>
        We look forward to seeing you on Monday (06/01) at Galvanize SF! If you
        have any questions, please reach out to Zach Latta at zach@hackedu.us
        or give him a call at 310-801-7309.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="section red text-center">
  <h1 class="open-sans"></h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-10 small-centered large-10 text-left columns">
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Personal Commitment</legend>
        <input id="checkbox1" type="checkbox">
        <label for="checkbox1">I will attend Hack Camp from 9:20am to 4:00pm
          Monday through Friday.</label>
      <br>
      <input id="checkbox2" type="checkbox">
      <label for="checkbox2"> If I cannot attend a session, a parent will let
        Hack Camp facilitators know as soon as possible.</label>
      <br>
      <input id="checkbox3" type="checkbox">
      <label for="checkbox3">I will be dropped from the program if I have 2
        excused absences.</label>
      <br>
      <input id="checkbox4" type="checkbox">
        <label for="checkbox4">I will bring a laptop.</label>
      <br>
      <input id="checkbox5" type="checkbox">
      <label for="checkbox5">I understand the deadline to pay my tuition for
        the program is 8pm, Tuesday the 26th.</label>
  </fieldset>
      <label>Student's T-shirt size</label>
      <input type="text" placeholder="S,M,L,etc.">
      <label>Parent's T-shirt size</label>
      <input type="text" placeholder="S,M,L,etc.">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% if @financial_aid %>
  <div class="section success white text-center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-10 small-centered columns">
      <p>
      We noticed you applied for financial aid. We know everyone's situation is
      different. Please reach out to us at (310)-801-7309 for a 15 minute call to
      help us understand what we can do to help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>
<div class="section red text-center">
  <h1 class="open-sans">Application payment</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <% if @paid %>
      <div class="small-centered columns">
      <h4>You've already paid!</h4>
    </div>
    <% else %>
      <div class="small-10 small-centered large-4 large-centered columns">
      <form action="/<%= @secret %>/charge" method="POST">
        <script
          src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
          data-key="<%= @stripe_publishable_key %>"
          data-amount="59500"
          data-name="hackEDU"
          data-description="Hack Camp tuition"
          data-image="/img/hackedu_letter_logo.png">
        </script>
      </form>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="contact section text-center">
  <h1 class="white">Any Questions?</h1>
  <p class="white">
  Please reach out! We can be reached anytime
  at <a href="mailto:summer@hackedu.us">summer@hackedu.us</a>.
  </p>
</div>
